<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> Etudes a': Clermont Ganneau Archeologie orientale جـ ٣، ص ٢٩٥.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> Historisch- to- M. Tomaschek Euphrat und pographisches vom o beren aus ost - Kappadokien , فى - Kiepert- Fests chrift، برلين سنة ١٨٩٨.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> Palestine under: G. le Strange , the Molsems ٢٧٤ - ٢٨٦.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> . Brockelmann فى Mitt. d. Sem f.Or Sprachen جـ ٤، ص ٢٢٨.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
